Terminais sem uso na gramática

    fVAL
    fEVAL
    fLENG
    cELSE
    fRESUTIL
    fENTATRANK
    fNUMGR
    fATRGR


Gramática

    0 $accept: input "end of file"

    1 input: expression

    2 expression: assigment
    3           | command
    4           | logicalOr
    5           | illegal

    6 logicalOr: logicalOr oOR logicalXor
    7          | logicalXor

    8 logicalXor: logicalXor oXOR logicalAnd
    9           | logicalAnd

   10 logicalAnd: logicalAnd oAND logicalNot
   11           | logicalAnd oNAND logicalNot
   12           | logicalNot

   13 logicalNot: oNOT logicalNot
   14           | relational

   15 relational: relational "<" additive
   16           | relational ">" additive
   17           | relational oLE additive
   18           | relational oGE additive
   19           | relational oEQ additive
   20           | relational oNE additive
   21           | additive

   22 additive: additive "+" multiplicative
   23         | additive "-" multiplicative
   24         | multiplicative

   25 multiplicative: multiplicative "*" power
   26               | multiplicative "/" power
   27               | power

   28 power: unary "^" power
   29      | unary

   30 unary: "-" unary
   31      | "+" unary
   32      | primary

   33 primary: number
   34        | function
   35        | "(" expression ")"
   36        | attribute
   37        | simulationResponse
   38        | simulationControl
   39        | variable
   40        | formula

   41 number: NUMD
   42       | NUMH

   43 command: commandIF
   44        | commandFOR

   45 commandIF: cIF "(" expression "," expression "," expression ")"
   46          | cIF "(" expression "," expression ")"

   47 commandFOR: cFOR variable "=" expression cTO expression cDO assigment
   48           | cFOR attribute "=" expression cTO expression cDO assigment

   49 function: mathFunction
   50         | trigonFunction
   51         | probFunction
   52         | kernelFunction
   53         | elementFunction
   54         | pluginFunction
   55         | userFunction

   56 kernelFunction: fTNOW
   57               | fTFIN
   58               | fMAXREP
   59               | fNUMREP
   60               | fIDENT
   61               | simulEntitiesWIP

   62 elementFunction: fTAVG "(" CSTAT ")"
   63                | fCOUNT "(" COUNTER ")"

   64 trigonFunction: fSIN "(" expression ")"
   65               | fCOS "(" expression ")"

   66 mathFunction: fROUND "(" expression ")"
   67             | fFRAC "(" expression ")"
   68             | fTRUNC "(" expression ")"
   69             | fEXP "(" expression ")"
   70             | fSQRT "(" expression ")"
   71             | fLOG "(" expression ")"
   72             | fLN "(" expression ")"
   73             | fMOD "(" expression "," expression ")"
   74             | mathMIN "(" expression "," expression ")"
   75             | mathMAX "(" expression "," expression ")"

   76 probFunction: fRND1
   77             | fEXPO "(" expression ")"
   78             | fNORM "(" expression "," expression ")"
   79             | fUNIF "(" expression "," expression ")"
   80             | fWEIB "(" expression "," expression ")"
   81             | fLOGN "(" expression "," expression ")"
   82             | fGAMM "(" expression "," expression ")"
   83             | fERLA "(" expression "," expression ")"
   84             | fTRIA "(" expression "," expression "," expression ")"
   85             | fBETA "(" expression "," expression "," expression "," expression ")"
   86             | fDISC "(" listaparm ")"

   87 userFunction: "USER" "(" expression ")"

   88 listaparm: listaparm "," expression "," expression
   89          | expression "," expression

   90 illegal: ILLEGAL

   91 attribute: ATRIB
   92          | ATRIB "[" expression "]"
   93          | ATRIB "[" expression "," expression "]"
   94          | ATRIB "[" expression "," expression "," expression "]"

   95 simulationResponse: SIMRESP

   96 simulationControl: SIMCTRL

   97 variable: VARI
   98         | VARI "[" expression "]"
   99         | VARI "[" expression "," expression "]"
  100         | VARI "[" expression "," expression "," expression "]"

  101 formula: FORM
  102        | FORM "[" expression "]"
  103        | FORM "[" expression "," expression "]"
  104        | FORM "[" expression "," expression "," expression "]"

  105 assigment: ATRIB "=" expression
  106          | ATRIB "[" expression "]" "=" expression
  107          | ATRIB "[" expression "," expression "]" "=" expression
  108          | ATRIB "[" expression "," expression "," expression "]" "=" expression
  109          | VARI "=" expression
  110          | VARI "[" expression "]" "=" expression
  111          | VARI "[" expression "," expression "]" "=" expression
  112          | VARI "[" expression "," expression "," expression "]" "=" expression

  113 pluginFunction: CTEZERO
  114               | fNQ "(" QUEUE ")"
  115               | fLASTINQ "(" QUEUE ")"
  116               | fFIRSTINQ "(" QUEUE ")"
  117               | fSAQUE "(" QUEUE "," ATRIB ")"
  118               | fAQUE "(" QUEUE "," NUMD "," ATRIB ")"
  119               | fMR "(" RESOURCE ")"
  120               | fNR "(" RESOURCE ")"
  121               | fRESSEIZES "(" RESOURCE ")"
  122               | fSTATE "(" RESOURCE ")"
  123               | fIRF "(" RESOURCE ")"
  124               | fSETSUM "(" SET ")"
  125               | fNUMSET "(" SET ")"


